## ğŸ”§ Development Configuration

### Default Ports
- **Host**: http://localhost:8080
- **Remote**: http://localhost:8081

## ğŸ“š Useful Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pnpm dev` | Start both services in development mode |
| `pnpm build` | Build both projects for production |
| `pnpm run host:dev` | Start only the host |
| `pnpm run remote:dev` | Start only the remote |

